locality: Laderas boscosas y filas al sur del Salto Maria Espuma (Salto Ichun) a lo largo del rio Ichun, tributario del rio Paragua. Base of slopes above river bank. Leaves firmly membranous, rich green above, pale green below.

Depto. Atabapo: Laderas que miran al suroeste, cabeceras del rio Iguapo, sector meridional de la Meseta Sur-Este, bosque enano musgoso con ramas semidecumbentes y entrecruzadas. Along stream above waterfall.

Summit of Tafelberg. Along trail from camp on upper Augustus Creek to Arrowhead Basin, ca. 100 m from rim of basin. Bamboo (Arthrostylidium scandens McClure, Evans 3302) thicket (ca. 10 m x 20 m) growing beneath low primary forest (canopy ca. 20 m tall).
3 km s of el puaji; morichal
